Package: davis-wx
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-venv, adduser, xdg-utils, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Davis Weather Station monitoring and display
 Web-based dashboard for Davis Vantage Pro2/Vue weather stations.
 Includes a serial logger daemon and FastAPI web application.
 .
 After installation, open "Davis Weather Station" from the application
 menu or browse to http://localhost:8000.
